\|J_{\ell}(u^{*})\|_{0,\ell}\|e-I_{h}^{c}e\|_{0,\ell}\nonumber\\
&&~~~~~~+|\int\limits_{\partial\Omega}(\lambda_{k} u-
\widehat{\lambda}_{k,h_{l}} u^{*})e|+ |\sum\limits_{j=k}^{k+q-1}
a(u_{k}^{h_{l}}, u_{j,h_{l}})(
